com.facebook.buck.rules.modern

Interface ClassInfo<T extends Buildable>

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    DefaultClassInfo

    public interface ClassInfo<T extends Buildable>
    ClassInfo is used by ModernBuildRule to extract information from a Buildable instance. It computes various things (rulekeys, deps, etc) by iterating over all the fields of the Buildable.
